          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The Pu-239 and U-235 conversion targets were placed",
                "on the collimated neutron beam. The three types of",
                "indicator foils were metal aluminum, quartz crystal",
                "and mixture of (NH4)2HPO4 and pure paraffin. The",
                "intensity of neutron on the indicator foil was about",
                "1E8 n/cm2/s."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "LONGC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The beta counting device included bell shaped",
                "Geiger beta counter, high voltage stabilized power",
                "supply and scaler. The stability was tested using a",
                "U3O8 standard beta source."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "PART-DET": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "B"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Four dosimetry reactions were selected to",
                "determine the parameter beta(239Pu), which are",
                "31P(n,p)31Si, 27Al(n,p)27Mg, 28Si(n,p)28Al and",
                "27Al(n,a)24Na, the half-life of the reaction products",
                "are 2.62 hours, 9.5 minutes, 2.3 minutes and 15",
                "hours. The indicator foils were removed after two",
                "hours irradiation, then the beta radioactivity of the",
                "reaction products were measured, the Al indicator",
                "foils were measured after cooling for 25 minutes."
              ]
            }
          ],
